text: An old shop selling their banding herbal anti pain oil. Friendly and honest staffs.

A smooth transaction, I am not sure if there are other uncles looking after the shop but  the uncle I met is friendly. No price list as mentioned in many reviews and I got my pain relief oil at SGD 12.

The staff (uncle) very RUDE & BAD ATTITUDE to my mum (83 year old) during purchase the medical oil this morning. He can talk to my mum nicely, is not telling my mum... return back the money... want to buy ...buy ... and yet I did called my mum ask her pass the phone to uncle. He ignore to answer .... just want to make sure my mum purchase the right item . I'm so angry ... call direct to the shop and yet the uncle tell me off and hang up the phone .... SO RUDE ..... Very disappointed !!!!
